      <Content>&lt;p&gt;Created in 1990 by Guido van Rossum who now works at Google.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Supports OO and structured programming.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;“A quick and light language”&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Doesn’t have a really heavy type system.&amp;#160; Similar to Ruby, Perl, bash&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;python.org to download windows installer&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;good easy video tutorial: &lt;a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Mf0h3HphEA"&gt;http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Mf0h3HphEA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Python_96DC/image_2.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Python_96DC/image_thumb.png" width="310" height="380" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;should have been print (“Hello World”)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.tutorialspoint.com/python/python_tutorial.pdf"&gt;http://www.tutorialspoint.com/python/python_tutorial.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;google python &lt;a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tKTZoB2Vjuk"&gt;http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tKTZoB2Vjuk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://thepythongamebook.com/en:start"&gt;http://thepythongamebook.com/en:start&lt;/a&gt; – python game book&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://inventwithpython.com/"&gt;http://inventwithpython.com/&lt;/a&gt; – invent games in python… looks good!&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Hello World&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;print (“hello world”)&amp;#160; - as I’m using python 3.x&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Python_96DC/image_4.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; pad